Monitoring and Maintenance
Production Monitoring:
monitoring:
  metrics:
    - system.cpu.usage
    - system.memory.usage
    - app.request.latency
    - app.error.rate
    - user.active.count
  
  alerts:
    - condition: app.error.rate > 5%
      action: [email, slack]
      severity: critical
    
    - condition: system.cpu.usage > 80%
      action: [auto_scale]
      severity: warning
  
  logging:
    level: info
    retention: 30 days
    analysis: real-time
Maintenance Schedule:
●	Daily: System health checks, backup verification
●	Weekly: Security updates, performance optimization
●	Monthly: Feature releases, database maintenance
●	Quarterly: Security audits, disaster recovery testing
Support System Implementation
Multi-tier Support Structure:
Tier 1: Automated Support
  - Chatbot for common questions
  - Knowledge base access
  - Community forum

Tier 2: Human Support
  - Email support (24-hour response)
  - Phone support (8 AM - 8 PM)
  - In-app chat support

Tier 3: Technical Support
  - Technical issue resolution
  - Bug investigation
  - Feature requests

