Appendix B: Glossary
Agro-ecological Zone: Geographic area with similar climate, soil, and agricultural potential
Crop Rotation: Practice of growing different crops sequentially on same land
Disease Incidence: Percentage of plants affected by disease
Extension Service: Government program providing agricultural advice to farmers
Integrated Pest Management: Ecosystem-based strategy focusing on long-term prevention
Market Intelligence: Information about market conditions, prices, and trends
Precision Agriculture: Farming management concept using technology to optimize returns
Yield Gap: Difference between potential and actual crop yields
Appendix C: Risk Assessment Matrix
Risk	Probability	Impact	Mitigation Strategy
Low farmer adoption	Medium	High	Community engagement, training, free basic features
AI recommendation errors	Low	High	Expert validation, confidence scores, farmer override
Internet connectivity issues	High	Medium	Offline functionality, SMS fallback, data optimization
Data privacy concerns	Medium	High	Strong encryption, clear policies, user control
Funding shortfalls	Medium	High	Diversified revenue streams, phased development
Technical scalability issues	Low	High	Cloud infrastructure, auto-scaling, load testing
Content accuracy problems	Medium	High	Expert validation, user feedback, regular updates
Regulatory compliance issues	Low	High	Legal review, government partnerships, compliance audits
